{"tid":413596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南加州大學專家：自殺是疾病","createTime":"2017-09-25T14:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T14:16:50.000Z","uid":44725,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd96716e78a47fd76443f53b1fb413bca814388","tid":413596,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"關注自殺問題的南加州大學醫學專家杰克遜（Luke Jackson）指出，不少證據顯示自殺傾向可能是疾病，自殺者因大腦受損而無法保護自己，並非單純是意志薄弱的問題。 <br />\n<br />\n專家指出，自殺者會有不少徵兆，例如較多喝酒服藥、睡眠習慣改變、特意與人道別等，情緒上亦會較焦慮憂鬱。惟由於自殺被污名化，例如被視作自私或不負責任行為，令受困者多不願求助，旁人則擔心談論自殺可能會觸發自殺念頭而不敢多問，錯過援助時機。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170915/s00014/1505411835788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170915%2Fs00014%2F1505411835788&d=XPJFyjIw5KXs1tGco9R6fAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=59963557\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170915%2Fs00014%2F1505411835788&h=05738452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170915/s00014/1505411835788</a>"},{"pid":"a6a145319be6c9cb4dcbf43a5116a060e07698ef","tid":413596,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"會唔會傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f74feeb0db74bec3db9e19918c004d3aa98a20","tid":413596,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2d8a7059cac9eba9edffcfaad6fd039515972b","tid":413596,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"樓主要傾訴下？"},{"pid":"8282fc68483b586e8b61d834ebeee9503b1eda6c","tid":413596,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會傳染<im